https://www.w3schools.com/tags/ref_canvas.asp

Beispiele Farbwerte setzen:

c.fillStyle = "orange";
c.fillStyle = "#FFA500";
c.fillStyle = "rgb(255,165,0)";
c.fillStyle = "rgba(255,165,0,1)";



Colors, Styles, and Shadows:

c.fillStyle="#FF0000";
c.strokeStyle="#FF0000";
c.shadowColor="black";
c.shadowBlur=20;
c.shadowOffsetX=20;
c.shadowOffsetY=20;